```matlab
% Load and preprocess image
img = imread('environment_image.jpg');
grayImg = rgb2gray(img);

% Edge detection for obstacle identification
edges = edge(grayImg, 'Canny');

% Object detection using regionprops
stats = regionprops(binaryImg, 'Area', 'Centroid', 'BoundingBox');

% Display results
figure;
imshow(img);
hold on;
for k = 1:length(stats)

end
```

```matlab

% Display results
```
